import React from 'react'; import Lottie from 'lottie-react'; import not from '../assets/not.json'; const Notification = () => { return (
{/* Lottie animation */}
{/* Category 1 */} ( < div className = "flex flex-wrap justify-center" > {data.map((item, index) => ( < div key = {index} className = "bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4 w-64 text-center" > < h5 className = "text-xl font-bold leading-none text-gray-900 dark:text-white" > Category: {item.category} < p className = "text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white" > Username: {item.username} < p className = "text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white" > Game ID: {item.game_id} < p className = "text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white" > Selected: {item.selected} < p className = "text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white" > Winner: {item.winner} ))} );
); }; export default Notification;
